##################################
     COMPILATION (LINUX ONLY)
##################################

GFORTRAN and openMPI  compilers must be installed before attempting 
to compile the MultiWell package.

In the current directory type:

make

The code will be compiled and the binaries will be put in ./bin
They may then be copied (or linked) to a directory in PATH 
like /usr/local/bin.

##################################
           TESTING
##################################

The MultiWell tools may be tested after compilation by:

1) Typing: ./runtest_all from the /scripts directory.

 
